{"tid":2179024,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"點解政府會喺自願檢測前夕放寬限聚？","createTime":"2020-08-28T21:24:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T14:12:32.000Z","uid":61122,"like":16,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9e80ca5506d4b5ee0043ef9a99421af240bddd64","tid":2179024,"uid":61122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T21:24:48.000Z","msg":"好簡單，想爆多波之後用嚟做藉口強制檢驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出面啲隱形患者多到你唔信，同埋<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">政府係冇任何措施限制佢哋所有行動，完全講個信字</span></span><br />\n<br />\n一個家庭有一個發病，得果個要入camp，親密到幾歲既仔發燒，當懷疑入院，<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">佢父母都可以照樣如常返屋企，真係有病徵佢哋自己報先會入院</span></span><br />\n<br />\n仲有，不斷有支那人過嚟，佢哋係有香港身分證，佢哋係冇病徵就覺自己冇事，香港多鳩餘搞咁多嘢佢又有健康碼，<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">然撚後周撚圍走</span></span>，最後一有病徵先報衛生署。<br />\n<br />\n所以，政府放寬係<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">唔撚可信</span></span>，無論自願檢測同放寬限聚，都係一個局，局個健康碼出嚟，局你DNA送中。<br />\n<br />\n求鳩大家放寬都唔好周圍去，一日未有疫苗，個疫情都未完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ce3c4fbd062f7c375c81eaf53f4fa6c371fdb6d","tid":2179024,"uid":61122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T21:24:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"944cc79065615d0f6cb7134ae50b9571c793a4a6","tid":2179024,"uid":61122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T21:25:08.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"95230c868cea0eccbb545c5233aebfe37d513a55","tid":2179024,"uid":61122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T21:30:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5c00455ad9765cc1bdbe2e2514ffe0205153929f","tid":2179024,"uid":61122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T21:43:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab53148a892af5ad69042e43ead1d28e014856b1","tid":2179024,"uid":61122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T23:49:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f35a3255f0c9cbb26462245986a2a6a0bc5f893","tid":2179024,"uid":165028,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T01:20:04.000Z","msg":"會唔會太陰謀論"},{"pid":"56220beea3330ccb8b2bf0da533ac8fe600351b6","tid":2179024,"uid":61122,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"1f35a3255f0c9cbb26462245986a2a6a0bc5f893","tid":2179024,"uid":165028,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T01:20:04.000Z","msg":"會唔會太陰謀論"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T01:31:02.000Z","msg":"陰謀論？政府點應對大家有眼睇，宜家就算確診都要等一兩日先送院，一兩日入面個patient做咩都冇人阻到<br />\n<br />\n唔係陰謀論，係根本未安全，防疫漏洞大，好似冇防咁"},{"pid":"c864834cee56306362c66a15cf92c73705e26d36","tid":2179024,"uid":30293,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T01:34:32.000Z","msg":"未放寛都周街都係人啦<br />\n講經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nDonki打晒蛇餅 商場人頭湧湧 郊外逼過西"},{"pid":"df9164960a8a67d932b2b19b311e8c274c08343b","tid":2179024,"uid":61122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c864834cee56306362c66a15cf92c73705e26d36","tid":2179024,"uid":30293,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T01:34:32.000Z","msg":"未放寛都周街都係人啦<br />\n講經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nDonki打晒蛇餅 商場人頭湧湧 郊外逼過西"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T02:08:01.000Z","msg":"呼籲大家唔好鬆懈，好危險"},{"pid":"e8aef3d908039077156feb37eb6de09723a9bc15","tid":2179024,"uid":48362,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T02:11:44.000Z","msg":"無左#7 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a716734484e36d926a414cdcee719ed46bdec931","tid":2179024,"uid":120487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f35a3255f0c9cbb26462245986a2a6a0bc5f893","tid":2179024,"uid":165028,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":